data.description: Beautiful well maintained 3 bedrooms, 2 Bath home located in a quiet neighborhood, in the Grays Creek School District. This home features a formal dining room, Stainless Steel Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Microwave, Range and LVP flooring throughout the house. Only carpet in the walk in closet in the Master Suite. Water Softener, New Fence, New Shower in Master Bathroom, New Storm Door, New Concrete Pad in the backyard, Gazebo and Solar Panels. This home has so much to offer. Don't miss your chance.  Schedule your viewing today!!!
